snippet.title: beatmania APPEND GOTTAMIX2 ~Going Global~ (PlayStation / 2000) - Gameplay
snippet.description:
Decided to take a break from AC beatmania and try something I've never played, so here's beatmania APPEND GOTTAMIX2 ~Going Global~, emulated via Mednafen 0.9.41.

1:54 Moloko - Sing It Back (Can 7 Supermarket (Radio Edit)) [CLASSIC GARAGE]
4:20 Togo Project feat. Sana - サナ・モレッテ・ネ・エンテ [CUBAN GROOVE]
6:52 Ruff Driverz - Dreaming [BALEARIC ANTHEM]
9:06 Macky - Z.O.E (gamelan minimal mix) [GAMELAN MINIMAL]
12:04 Togo Project feat. Megu & Scotty D. - Sunshine Dance (Latino YOKAN-Mix) [CARNIVAL]
14:54 Moir & Mac - Going Global [EURO HOUSE]
16:54 PCM - fresh!! [NATIVE SCHOOL'S BREAKIN']
19:33 Little Big Bee - Centralization [AFRO TRIBAL HOUSE]
22:34 Credits

If there are any specific songs you want to see, let me know.
